instructions:
Analyze the following onboarding request and produce a role profile.


  {product}
  {role}
  {experience_level}
  {focus_areas}
  {tech_stack}


Rules:
- primary_concerns: exactly 5 items, ordered by importance for this role
- relevant_doc_topics: 8-12 search queries that will retrieve the most useful documentation chunks
- excluded_topics: topics that are irrelevant to this role (e.g. a backend dev doesn't need iOS SDK docs)
- learning_objectives: 4-6 concrete skills, each starting with an action verb (Implement, Configure, Debug, etc.)
- complexity_ceiling: "conceptual" for PMs/leads, "hands-on" for intermediate devs, "deep-dive" for advanced/security engineers
